data.description: Welcome to this beautiful sun filled 2 bedroom 2 bathroom condo in Takoma Park, MD and conveniently located near the DC border. This unit features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, hardwood floors and carpeted bedrooms. The condo also features in-unit washer and dryer as well as additional laundry facilities on each floor of the building. The unit conveys an assigned parking space along with plenty of guest parking available. All amenities and utilities are included in the condo fee such as central air conditioning, pool, tennis court, playground, picnic area, private dog park and community garden. No VA/FHA financing.
